FBIS4-8096 "dreeu069_i_94048" FBIS-EEU-94-069 Daily Report 11 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Expected Aid Convoys Fail To Arrive Expected Aid Convoys Fail To Arrive LD1104120994 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in Serbo-Croatian 1115 GMT 11 Apr 94 LD1104120994 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service Serbo-Croatian BFN [Excerpt] Zvornik, 11 Apr (TANJUG) -- No humanitarian or logistical convoys have arrived on the left [western] bank of the River Drina today, and no convoys went in the other direction, toward the territory of the Federal Republic of Yugoslavia, TANJUG's correspondent has learned from the command of the Zvornik garrison of the Bosnian Serb republic army. The same source says that several humanitarian and logistical convoys announced their arrival for today, and the Serb side granted them permission to cross the territory of the Serb republic. However, they have failed to arrive, and officials in Zvornik have not received any official explanation for this. [passage omitted]
